OL,3,CHospice boss makes 'devastating'
OL,4,Cdecision to cut back end-of-life
OL,5,Cservices
OL,7,FThe clinical director of a Devon
OL,8,Fhospice has made the "heartbreaking"
OL,9,Fdecision to cut back some end-of-life
OL,10,Fservices.
OL,12,FHospiscare in Exeter is facing a #2.5
OL,13,Fmillion deficit after being impacted
OL,14,Fby rising costs and a drop in
OL,15,Fdonations due to the ongoing cost of
OL,16,Fliving.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/10
