OL,3,CHospice boss makes 'devastating'
OL,4,Cdecision to cut back end-of-life
OL,5,Cservices
OL,7,FThe hospice, which provides vital end
OL,8,Fof life care for 1,000 square miles of
OL,9,Fthe county, receives 15% of its
OL,10,Ffunding from its local NHS body -
OL,11,Flower than the national average of 27%.
OL,13,FEarlier this year, the hospice's
OL,14,Fmanagement team made the decision to
OL,15,Fcut the number of beds on the ward by
OL,16,Fa third and is now having to make
OL,17,Ffurther cuts. This will likely result
OL,18,Fin staff redundancies.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/10
