OL,3,CHospice boss makes 'devastating'
OL,4,Cdecision to cut back end-of-life
OL,5,Cservices
OL,7,FAnn Rhys, the hospice's clinical
OL,8,Fdirector, said: "We're now in a
OL,9,Fposition that from September, our
OL,10,FHospice at Home teams across our
OL,11,Fgeography are needing to close.
OL,13,F"We are replacing it with a much
OL,14,Fsmaller rapid response service however
OL,15,Fbecause the team is smaller they'll no
OL,16,Flonger be able to hold them for a long
OL,17,Fperiod of time.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/10
