OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F435A1721050877
OL,3,CHospice boss makes 'devastating'
OL,4,Cdecision to cut back end-of-life
OL,5,Cservices
OL,7,F"We'll care for people in those teams
OL,8,Ffor about 72 hours and then we'll need
OL,9,Fto forward them on to acute NHS
OL,10,Fservices, our own community teams or
OL,11,Ffor people to come into our inpatient
OL,12,Funit here.
OL,14,F"It's absolutely devastating to be
OL,15,Fpulling back on our services."
OL,17,FAs well as Sarah Smith leading the
OL,18,Fhospice's public fundraising team, her
OL,19,Fgrandmother, Joan, received care at
OL,20,Fhome during her final days.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/10
