OL,3,CHospice boss makes 'devastating'
OL,4,Cdecision to cut back end-of-life
OL,5,Cservices
OL,7,F"They allowed her to die in the way
OL,8,Fthat she lived, which was gently,
OL,9,Fhumbly, quietly. And it was a real
OL,10,Fgift for the family for her to have
OL,11,Fthat.
OL,13,FDespite NHS Devon giving Hospiscare a
OL,14,Fone-off payment of #480,000 to help
OL,15,Fwith this year's financial challenges,
OL,16,FSarah said it will not prevent
OL,17,Fservices being cut back.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/10
