OL,3,CHospice boss makes 'devastating'
OL,4,Cdecision to cut back end-of-life
OL,5,Cservices
OL,7,F"It breaks my heart that our services
OL,8,Fare under any threat because the
OL,9,Ffinancial situation we find ourselves
OL,10,Fin is nothing to do with the beautiful
OL,11,Fway we're supported by our local
OL,12,Fcommunity.
OL,14,F"We are such a well-loved charity and
OL,15,Fwe are so grateful for the support
OL,16,Fthat we receive.
OL,18,F"This is an inequity in the funding
OL,19,Fthat we receive. It is heartbreaking
OL,20,Fbut also makes me angry," Sarah said.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/10
