OL,3,CHospice boss makes 'devastating'
OL,4,Cdecision to cut back end-of-life
OL,5,Cservices
OL,7,FA spokesperson for NHS Devon said: "We
OL,8,Frecognise the high-level of care
OL,9,Fhospice teams across the county
OL,10,Fprovide to patients and their families
OL,11,Fat a hugely emotional time in their
OL,12,Flives.
OL,14,F"Each year, we provide financial
OL,15,Fsupport to Hospiscare through grant
OL,16,Ffunding. The hospice has flexibility
OL,17,Fto invest their grant in the services
OL,18,Fwhich best meet the needs of their
OL,19,Flocal community."
OL,26,@vD@AOU
