OL,3,CHospice boss makes 'devastating'
OL,4,Cdecision to cut back end-of-life
OL,5,Cservices
OL,7,F"The NHS in Devon faces severe
OL,8,Ffinancial challenges ` for the last
OL,9,Ftwo years we have recorded a deficit
OL,10,Fof more than #40 million and this year
OL,11,Fwe forecast a deficit of #80 million -
OL,12,Fand we are having to take difficult
OL,13,Fdecisions on spending.
OL,15,F"We recognise many hospices locally
OL,16,Fand nationwide have faced financial
OL,17,Fchallenges arising from reduced public
OL,18,Fdonations due to the cost-of-living
OL,19,Fcrisis.
OL,26,@wD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/10
