OL,3,CHospice boss makes 'devastating'
OL,4,Cdecision to cut back end-of-life
OL,5,Cservices
OL,7,F"Despite our ongoing financial
OL,8,Fchallenges, we were pleased to agree
OL,9,Fan extra #480,000 for Hospiscare for
OL,10,F2024/25.
OL,12,F"We are currently working with local
OL,13,Fpartners, including the hospices, to
OL,14,Fdevelop a Devon-wide commissioning
OL,15,Fplan for end of life care across the
OL,16,Fcounty."
